name: ComProbe Analyzer Capture File
summary: A CFA file is a data capture file created by Frontline ComProbe analyzers, such as the BPA 600 Dual Mode Bluetooth Protocol Analyzer and the BPA Low Energy Bluetooth Protocol Analyzer. It contains data collected by an analyzer such as the frame number, command, segment, block, or UUID. CFA files are collected by analyzers to determine if a product meets Bluetooth interoperability standards.
